{"tid":404184,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"又係爭仔　江蘇兩女街頭互毆撕剩底衫褲","createTime":"2017-09-18T00:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:34:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d025786f80f68b38bd9a5c529fc67e266fe0f6c2","tid":404184,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"內地再傳出女子因感情糾紛決鬥街頭的視頻，江蘇省常州市金壇區2名年輕女子當街互毆，其中一方還被拖行在地，遭對方怒扯只剩褲子和半開的內衣，似乎被打到不省人事。不過更令人心寒的是儘管四周有不少民衆圍觀，但卻沒有人上前制止。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170916__PL__%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%8601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170916__PL__%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%2592%25E6%25AF%258601.jpg&h=029003bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n <br />\n畫面中，2名辣妹當街互毆，其中一名身穿黑色衣服的女子強拉對方衣服，還一邊拖行、猛踹頭部，行為相當潑辣。躺在地上的女子幾近半裸，無力反抗癱坐在地，後來又被拖下緊身短裙，露出內褲，一旁則是有不少民眾圍觀，但都沒有人出手援助。警方接獲消息，迅速趕往現場阻止鬧劇，但案發原因還有待進一步調查。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170916__PL__%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%8603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170916__PL__%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%2592%25E6%25AF%258603.jpg&h=40b504c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170916__PL__%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%8602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170916__PL__%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%2592%25E6%25AF%258602.jpg&h=8c1f045f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據爆料者稱，事發在13日，地點常州金壇東站一間KTV門口，兩名年輕女子因為爭仔發生爭執。該視頻在網上熱傳，網民紛紛概嘆當下年輕人出手太狠:「現在動不動就扒衣服了，女人對女人下手更狠！」；「有甚麼難解的矛盾，採取如此過激的行為，看來問題是難以調和了！不管如何，都希望冷靜處理！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/2417746-%E5%8F%88%E4%BF%82%E7%88%AD%E4%BB%94-%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%85%A9%E5%A5%B3%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%86%E6%92%95%E5%89%A9%E5%BA%95%E8%A1%AB%E8%A4%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-plastic-post%2F2417746-%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25BF%2582%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25BA%2592%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2592%2595%25E5%2589%25A9%25E5%25BA%2595%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A4%25B2&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e62ea5a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/2417746-%E5%8F%88%E4%BF%82%E7%88%AD%E4%BB%94-%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E5%85%A9%E5%A5%B3%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E4%BA%92%E6%AF%86%E6%92%95%E5%89%A9%E5%BA%95%E8%A1%AB%E8%A4%B2</a>"},{"pid":"f7ed529a539a15f3ad1aa2c7ca27d2a3cfe8dca9","tid":404184,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"見怪不怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60667565625c4e089db6a1f7964544f0bc0aca54","tid":404184,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:09:46.000Z","msg":"點解支那人打交咁鐘意扯爛衫褲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967ab0d6d4c12a538de44fef729d7a069449db9b","tid":404184,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:10:39.000Z","msg":"有鋪除衫癮"},{"pid":"0e6431d710277cb7fa982e07d3fdd31a96976cf1","tid":404184,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"條仔肯定醜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985fb54ad1dd4a4259dfb93884cc1237d49bc081","tid":404184,"uid":34503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解支那人打交咁鐘意扯爛衫褲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為啲衫褲係中國製"}]}